FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our house-making app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the house-making app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app guides you through the process of designing and planning your dream home, from layout to finishes, using intuitive tools and expert advice.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Can I customize my house design?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! Our app offers a wide range of customization options for floor plans, architectural styles, materials, and interior design elements.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is the app suitable for beginners?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, our app is designed to be user-friendly for both beginners and experienced designers, with tutorials and tips to help you along the way.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I get cost estimates for my house design?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, our app provides approximate cost estimates based on your design choices, materials, and location to help you plan your budget.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I share my house designs?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: You can easily share your designs with friends, family, or professionals through the app, exporting them in various formats or generating 3D walkthroughs.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About House Creation
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the house-making app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app uses advanced AI and design algorithms to create custom house plans based on your preferences, budget, and lot specifications. Simply input your requirements, and watch as your dream home takes shape!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I customize the house designs?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! Our app offers a wide range of customization options, from architectural styles to interior layouts. You can modify room sizes, add features, and even experiment with different materials to create your perfect home.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How long does it take to generate a house design?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: The initial design is generated within minutes. However, you can spend as much time as you like refining and adjusting the design to meet your exact specifications. Our real-time rendering allows you to see changes instantly.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Are the house designs suitable for construction?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our app produces detailed, construction-ready blueprints. These designs comply with standard building codes and can be directly used by contractors. However, we recommend having a local architect or engineer review the plans to ensure they meet specific local regulations.
